#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst:71 20e51aaececb475788b9fe571b682932
msgid "Initialise the CAN bus with the given parameters."
msgstr "使用给定参数初始化 CAN 总线。"

#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst 591f56384c63426eaadb08b1043298e4
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "参数"

#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst:73 d563e09dab20498ca1f99d976aa9e0c2
msgid "The CAN bus ID."
msgstr "CAN 总线 ID。"

#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst:74 9a9664962e5548869243ff3a1b9f59d0
msgid "One of NORMAL, NO_ACKNOWLEDGE, LISTEN_ONLY."
msgstr "NORMAL、NO_ACKNOWLEDGE、LISTEN_ONLY 之一。"

#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst:75 16421f4599a7422f923d3301748857b3
msgid "The pin to use for transmitting data."
msgstr "用于发送数据的引脚。"

#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst:76 223553375b3c49fa8200715666ecdc6f
msgid "The pin to use for receiving data."
msgstr "用于接收数据的引脚。"

#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst:77 e67c75b9799f4076aaae6d4d3b6a466c
msgid ""
"The value by which the CAN input clock is divided to generate the nominal"
" bit time quanta. Value between 1 and 1024 inclusive for classic CAN."
msgstr ""
"用于分频 CAN 输入时钟以生成标称位时间量子的值。对于经典 CAN，取值范围为 1 至 1024（含）。"

#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst:78 765ff4f925b34e53bb1b9b597909f61b
msgid ""
"The resynchronisation jump width in units of time quanta for nominal "
"bits; value between 1 and 4 inclusive for classic CAN."
msgstr ""
"标称位的重同步跳跃宽度（单位为时间量子）；对于经典 CAN，取值范围为 1 至 4（含）。"

#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst:79 dd5664b451fb490db4ce87a6919f5803
msgid ""
"Defines the location of the sample point in units of the time quanta for "
"nominal bits; value between 1 and 16 inclusive for classic CAN."
msgstr ""
"定义标称位采样点的位置（单位为时间量子）；对于经典 CAN，取值范围为 1 至 16（含）。"

#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst:80 13a5627010b94e3c9dc960db2491dd24
msgid ""
"Defines the location of the transmit point in units of the time quanta "
"for nominal bits; value between 1 and 8 inclusive for classic CAN."
msgstr ""
"定义标称位发送点的位置（单位为时间量子）；对于经典 CAN，取值范围为 1 至 8（含）。"

#: ../../source/hardware/pwrcan.rst:81 c070c3ad1cb5450db5cd1ba7dd3643a4
msgid "Enables triple sampling when the TWAI controller samples a bit."
msgstr "在 TWAI 控制器采样位时启用三重采样。"

